1. DEFINITIONS
================================================================================

"Software" means the GuardForge backend, dashboard, SDKs, scripts, documentation,
and any updates or upgrades thereof, as distributed by MAXIA Lab.

"License Key" means the unique identifier issued by MAXIA Lab upon purchase
that authorizes use of a specific tier of the Software.

"Cloud Edition" means the version of the Software hosted by MAXIA Lab and
accessed via subscription.

"Self-Hosted Edition" means the version of the Software that Licensee installs
and runs on infrastructure under Licensee's control.

"Production Use" means use of the Software in any environment that processes
data of real users, customers, or in any commercial capacity.

"Internal Business Use" means use of the Software by Licensee's employees,
contractors, or subsidiaries solely for Licensee's own business operations.

